<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 14:05:54 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>“当我的演讲被称为反犹太主义时，我感到震惊”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-02-28/ty-article-magazine/.premium/when-my-speech-was-called-antisemitic-i-was-shocked/0000018d-efc4-dd8a-a5af-effe1d7c0000</link><description>获得柏林电影节最佳纪录片奖本应是以色列电影制片人尤瓦尔·亚伯拉罕职业生涯的顶峰。对《No Other Land》获奖感言的回应让他感到震惊，但他并没有陷入沉默</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 13:27:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-02-28/ty-article-magazine/.premium/when-my-speech-was-called-antisemitic-i-was-shocked/0000018d-efc4-dd8a-a5af-effe1d7c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军公布了两名在加沙北部战斗中丧生的以色列军官的名字</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-28/ty-article/.premium/idf-names-two-israeli-officers-killed-in-northern-gaza-fighting/0000018d-ef6e-d401-a3dd-ef7e03ae0000</link><description>Iftah Shahar 少校，25 岁​​，Cap。吉瓦蒂旅 24 岁的伊泰·赛义夫 (Itai Seif) 在简易爆炸装置被触发时身亡。以色列国防军称，另外七名士兵也在爆炸中受重伤</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 13:17:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-28/ty-article/.premium/idf-names-two-israeli-officers-killed-in-northern-gaza-fighting/0000018d-ef6e-d401-a3dd-ef7e03ae0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列地方选举：极端正统派、极右派在全国各地取得进展</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-28/ty-article/.premium/israels-local-elections-ultra-orthodox-far-right-make-gains-across-country/0000018d-eec3-d7f4-a3dd-eecfa37b0000</link><description>极端正统派和极右宗教犹太复国主义政党将在耶路撒冷取得压倒性胜利，而南部城市米兹佩·拉蒙将迎来一位以极右观点闻名的利库德集团市长。特拉维夫和海法仍然是自由派的据点</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 10:32:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-28/ty-article/.premium/israels-local-elections-ultra-orthodox-far-right-make-gains-across-country/0000018d-eec3-d7f4-a3dd-eecfa37b0000</guid></item><item><title>极右翼以色列定居者因西岸暴力风险将继续被拘留，未经审判</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-28/ty-article/.premium/far-right-israeli-settler-to-remain-in-detention-without-trial-over-risk-of-violence/0000018d-ee97-d05b-addd-ee97659c0000</link><description>以色列国防部长决定，由于阿里尔·达尼诺 (Ariel Danino) 可能在约旦河西岸煽动暴力，继 10 月份初次拘留后，将再对其实施行政拘留三个月</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 09:51:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-28/ty-article/.premium/far-right-israeli-settler-to-remain-in-detention-without-trial-over-risk-of-violence/0000018d-ee97-d05b-addd-ee97659c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列和哈马斯之间的人质释放、停火谈判立场如何？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-28/ty-article/.premium/where-do-the-hostage-release-talks-between-israel-and-hamas-stand-what-are-the-gaps/0000018d-ec6b-dd0a-afcf-efff7b040000</link><description>以色列和哈马斯都有兴趣在下个月斋月开始前达成释放人质的协议，但尽管最近几天的乐观情绪仍然存在，但仍然存在许多障碍</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 04:02:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-28/ty-article/.premium/where-do-the-hostage-release-talks-between-israel-and-hamas-stand-what-are-the-gaps/0000018d-ec6b-dd0a-afcf-efff7b040000</guid></item><item><title>自加沙战争爆发以来，以色列国防军坦克至少五次在以色列境内误射</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-28/ty-article/.premium/idf-tanks-mistakenly-fired-inside-israeli-territory-at-least-five-times-since-start-of-war/0000018d-eb5e-d401-a3dd-eb5e50570000</link><description>有一次，以色列和黎巴嫩边境沿线的哈尼塔集体农场发射了两枚炮弹，炸毁了两栋房屋；另一次，在加沙发射的一枚炮弹击中了斯德洛特市政厅。以色列国防军回应：“吸取了必要的教训”</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 04:02:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-28/ty-article/.premium/idf-tanks-mistakenly-fired-inside-israeli-territory-at-least-five-times-since-start-of-war/0000018d-eb5e-d401-a3dd-eb5e50570000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯领导人呼吁在斋月期间向阿克萨清真寺进军；两名以色列国防军士兵在加沙丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-28/ty-article-live/sirens-sound-in-southern-israel-idf-strikes-hezbollah-targets-in-south-lebanon/0000018d-ed87-d7f4-a3dd-ef8fa5460000</link><description>什莫纳市的建筑遭到黎巴嫩发射的袭击 ■ 拜登表示，他希望下周能就停火达成一致 ■ 消息人士称，哈马斯正在研究涉及 40 天停火和交换人质的巴黎休战提议 ■ 哈马斯管理的卫生部称加沙最后一天有96人死亡</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 03:25:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-28/ty-article-live/sirens-sound-in-southern-israel-idf-strikes-hezbollah-targets-in-south-lebanon/0000018d-ed87-d7f4-a3dd-ef8fa5460000</guid></item><item><title>以色列第一家 Shake Shack 在特拉维夫开业，但理由并不稳固</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-27/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israels-first-shake-shack-opens-in-tel-aviv-on-shaky-grounds/0000018d-eb52-d1e0-a1dd-fbf7b4190000</link><description>在支持巴勒斯坦的呼吁抵制以及细心的犹太人的失望叹息中，以色列迎来了第一个 Shake Shack 汉堡店，这让我们的记者回忆起更简单、更俗气的时代</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 20:45:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-27/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israels-first-shake-shack-opens-in-tel-aviv-on-shaky-grounds/0000018d-eb52-d1e0-a1dd-fbf7b4190000</guid></item><item><title>加沙战争期间以色列地方选举投票率低，公众冷漠</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-27/ty-article/low-turnout-in-israels-local-elections-amid-war-in-gaza-public-apathy/0000018d-ec43-d05b-addd-eec305be0000</link><description>全天投票率仍然很低，只有不到一半的合格选民投票</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 20:42:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-27/ty-article/low-turnout-in-israels-local-elections-amid-war-in-gaza-public-apathy/0000018d-ec43-d05b-addd-eec305be0000</guid></item><item><title>这个斋月，以色列极右翼部长会放火还是会被遏制？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-02-27/ty-article/.highlight/this-ramadan-will-israels-far-right-ministers-set-fires-or-be-reined-in/0000018d-ebc0-d401-a3dd-ebda30fd0000</link><description>用你自己的混合比喻来说，看起来这种噪音不会在基地门口停止，格兰特先生。是时候遏制你们党的领导人拉拢的不负责任的行为者了</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 19:51:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-02-27/ty-article/.highlight/this-ramadan-will-israels-far-right-ministers-set-fires-or-be-reined-in/0000018d-ebc0-d401-a3dd-ebda30fd0000</guid></item><item><title>战争中的以色列：您需要了解的信息 – 第 144 天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-02-27/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-144/0000018d-eb6f-d401-a3dd-eb7f2a0f0000</link><description>拜登：如果达成释放人质/停火协议，以色列愿意在斋月期间停止加沙战斗，希望下周一能达成协议 ■ 一位以色列高级消息人士告诉美国广播公司新闻，内塔尼亚胡总理对拜登的言论感到惊讶 ■ 哈马斯官员称该组织正在研究巴黎制定的最新提案，但双方之间仍存在巨大差距 ■ 这是战争开始 144 天后您需要了解的内容</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 16:46:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-02-27/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-144/0000018d-eb6f-d401-a3dd-eb7f2a0f0000</guid></item><item><title>拜登可以依靠这两位以色列政客作为他的盟友吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-27/ty-article/.premium/can-biden-depend-on-these-two-israeli-politicians-to-be-his-allies/0000018d-eacb-d7f4-a3dd-eecfb42b0000</link><description>本尼·甘茨和加迪·艾森科特加入了以色列战时内阁，忙于减少错误决策并防止鲁莽决策。但他们现在会支持拜登对加沙和该地区的愿景，还是成为内塔尼亚胡的全职帮凶？</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 16:02:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-27/ty-article/.premium/can-biden-depend-on-these-two-israeli-politicians-to-be-his-allies/0000018d-eacb-d7f4-a3dd-eecfb42b0000</guid></item><item><title>对于流离失所的以色列青少年来说，荒野是寻找自我的完美场所</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-27/ty-article-magazine/.premium/for-displaced-israeli-teens-the-wilderness-is-proving-a-perfect-place-to-find-themselves/0000018d-ea2a-dc4b-a1cd-fb2f759e0000</link><description>约20万以色列人因战争而被疏散，青少年在孤立、焦虑和抑郁中挣扎。一项新举措旨在帮助他们逃离大自然</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 15:08:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-27/ty-article-magazine/.premium/for-displaced-israeli-teens-the-wilderness-is-proving-a-perfect-place-to-find-themselves/0000018d-ea2a-dc4b-a1cd-fb2f759e0000</guid></item><item><title>因恐怖袭击而在以色列服无期徒刑的巴勒斯坦作家获得阿拉伯文学最高奖提名</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-02-27/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-writer-jailed-in-israel-for-bombing-is-nominated-for-top-arab-literature-prize/0000018d-eab9-dc4b-a1cd-fbbdd23b0000</link><description>出生于纳布卢斯的巴森·卡达吉 (Basem Khadaqji) 于 2005 年因协助一名在特拉维夫杀害三名以色列人的自杀式炸弹袭击者而被定罪，在手稿被偷运出狱后，他在狱中出版了至少六本书</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 14:43:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-02-27/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-writer-jailed-in-israel-for-bombing-is-nominated-for-top-arab-literature-prize/0000018d-eab9-dc4b-a1cd-fbbdd23b0000</guid></item><item><title>右翼 MKs 不顾专业人士的意见，通过新法律扩大本·格维尔的权力</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-27/ty-article/.premium/far-right-mks-moving-to-extend-ben-gvirs-authority-with-new-law/0000018d-ea6c-d409-a1ff-ef7eb62d0000</link><description>根据该提案，国家安全部长将能够宣布一群人为犯罪组织，并让他们没收资产。司法部警告该法律将过多权力集中于一个政府机构</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 14:26:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-27/ty-article/.premium/far-right-mks-moving-to-extend-ben-gvirs-authority-with-new-law/0000018d-ea6c-d409-a1ff-ef7eb62d0000</guid></item><item><title>警方正在寻找周日以来失踪的以色列北部 9 岁女孩</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-27/ty-article/.premium/police-searching-for-nine-year-old-girl-from-northern-israel-missing-since-sunday/0000018d-ea56-dc4b-a1cd-fb7fceaa0000</link><description>三年前从埃塞俄比亚移民的海马诺特·卡绍(Haimanot Kassau)最后一次被人看见是在她居住的吸收中心的入口处。警方已收集安全录像和证词，但目前尚未找到任何线索</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 13:33:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-27/ty-article/.premium/police-searching-for-nine-year-old-girl-from-northern-israel-missing-since-sunday/0000018d-ea56-dc4b-a1cd-fb7fceaa0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列135,000名流离失所公民的悲剧</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-27/ty-article-magazine/.premium/what-makes-the-plight-of-israels-displaced-citizens-different/0000018d-ea95-d1e0-a1dd-fbf529ed0000</link><description>由于加沙战争，来自北方和南方的以色列人发现自己在自己的国家内流离失所，而且看不到任何明确的解决方案。 《国土报》采访了流离失所问题专家，了解其带来的挑战</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 13:29:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-27/ty-article-magazine/.premium/what-makes-the-plight-of-israels-displaced-citizens-different/0000018d-ea95-d1e0-a1dd-fbf529ed0000</guid></item><item><title>公共广播公司坎删除了以色列柏林电影节获奖者演讲反犹太主义标签的片段</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-27/ty-article/.premium/israels-public-broadcaster-removes-accusations-of-antisemitism-against-berlinale-winner/0000018d-ea27-d7f4-a3dd-ee2f193d0000</link><description>以色列电影导演尤瓦尔·亚伯拉罕的获奖感言提到了约旦河西岸受压迫的巴勒斯坦人，公共广播公司 Kan 称其为“反犹太主义”。亚伯拉罕的律师表示，自演讲发表以来，亚伯拉罕“收到了无数的威胁、死亡愿望和诅咒”</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 13:07:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-27/ty-article/.premium/israels-public-broadcaster-removes-accusations-of-antisemitism-against-berlinale-winner/0000018d-ea27-d7f4-a3dd-ee2f193d0000</guid></item><item><title>前以色列国防军副司令亚伊尔·戈兰将竞选工党领袖</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-27/ty-article/.premium/former-idf-chief-yair-golan-to-run-for-labor-party-leadership/0000018d-ea3a-d05b-addd-eebbf79e0000</link><description>这位前梅雷茨议员因10月7日勇敢的救援行动而声名鹊起，他正准备参加初选，以取代现任工党领袖梅拉夫·米凯利，打算“建立一个新的政治框架，团结整个自由派阵营”</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 12:25:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-27/ty-article/.premium/former-idf-chief-yair-golan-to-run-for-labor-party-leadership/0000018d-ea3a-d05b-addd-eebbf79e0000</guid></item><item><title>拜登表示以色列已准备好暂停加沙战斗；哈马斯称协议尚未完成</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-27/ty-article/biden-says-israel-is-ready-to-pause-gaza-fighting-hamas-says-deal-not-done-yet/0000018d-e991-d9a9-a1bd-ebbb67a00000</link><description>以色列代表团周一抵达卡塔尔继续会谈，美国总统乔·拜登在斋月之前公开设定下周在加沙达成停火协议的最后期限。然而，哈马斯否认已达成协议</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 11:36:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-27/ty-article/biden-says-israel-is-ready-to-pause-gaza-fighting-hamas-says-deal-not-done-yet/0000018d-e991-d9a9-a1bd-ebbb67a00000</guid></item></channel></rss>